Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used as a hint for reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the most mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:08.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is Nanki-Shirahama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:10.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The footprints of crime on a white sandy beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:11.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirahama Station\NJR Kinokuni Line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! Let's go check out souvenirs at the waiting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have to go look for souvenirs just yet, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, look! It's Mr. Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No surprise finding this in the plum-producing Kishu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's buy some on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so cute about a sour-looking guy like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nambo Kumakusunoki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's read Minakata Kumagusu Kinenkanâ€”\NMinakata Kumagusu Memorial Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a world-famous botanist who was born in Wakayama Prefecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,especially known for his research of plants and fungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they had a great researcher like that here, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd advise you to study a bit before travelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop by for a meal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crawfish here is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still a bit early...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check out the memorial hall first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Minakata Kumagusu Memorial Hall Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The road's closed on this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:58.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Minakata Kumagusu Memorial Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirarahama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, the sand is really fine and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it's so white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once heard that the secret of its whiteness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is that it's quartz sand consisting to 90% of silicate acid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. He sure knows a lot of trivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to take this sand home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, put it into a little bottle and carry it around with me, like you do with star sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go again with your girlish tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were looking at a weird keychain back at the station too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One with umeboshi attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron! Only brats like things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but aren't you Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! I'm a fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow! What a knockout!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the famous detective you all know, Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, could you take a picture of the two of us together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you come here to investigate a case or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. We're just sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won a raffle at the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all students?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're seniors at Naniwa Medical University.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're doctors in the making!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce everyone, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl next to you is the queen of our group, Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:08.66,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Maki Shinjo (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, cut it out, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next to her is our gigolo, Tatsuhiko Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiko Yura (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our Madonna, Madoka Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.08,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Madoka Mitsui (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's our whiz kid, Kanako Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kanako Miyahara (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kota Fuji (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm the clown of the group, Kota Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of them are in the art club,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and since Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} suggested we take a nature-sketching trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we all decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it's more like we're here to help Miss Rich Lady pass the time.{kanemochi o-jou-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about grateful, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She paid for the hotel, train tickets, and the rental car fee as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yura! You've got no class, talking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I broke up with her because I didn't like just what she's doing for all of us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, she spends hundreds of thousands of yen every month just on cosmetics...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time a new product goes on the market, she has it sent in from Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Madoka has no money, just like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and doesn't look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her childishness is a fly in the ointment though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you lucky, finding yourself a cutie-pie to go out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako, can you go get me something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go get it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be at your beck and call anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that thanks to you teaching me math,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which wasn't my strong point, during high-school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made it into university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do appreciate what you did for me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But would you stop bossing me around, harping on how grateful I should be to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to boss you around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've all come on this trip together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so why don't we all just go on and have a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll have Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} do things for me instead of Kanako from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it was that fainted during practical dissection practice, and was saved by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You promised you'd keep that a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be right back, so wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are your plans for after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to Shirahama Energy Land right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go to the underwater observatory
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Sandambeki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before finally watching the sunset from Senjojiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the morning, we're thinking of going to Adventure World...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come along with us, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks, we've already got plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the Shin'yuzaki Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, we'd better get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those people, you can't tell if they're getting along or not, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when you're young, anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:35.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sandambeki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really a bold sheer cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can go all the way to over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, why don't we go tour the caves, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can go down by elevator from that building over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that, we get to watch the sunset at Senjojiki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be super-beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:10:01.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Senjojiki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a magnificent view!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure glad we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was worth coming, just to see this sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to watch the sunset too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I've never seen the sunset from here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you like sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, why not stop over at the Tore Tore Market before going to Adventure World tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tore Tore Market?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from fresh seafood,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they have a whole line of top-quality locally-brewed sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say locally-brewed sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can send it home by courier service too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've also written the bus route to the market from Shin'yuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a bus stop called Bus Depot{...seriously? - Yep. Garage or car shed work too. XD} near the Tore Tore Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any buses that go directly from Tore Tore Market to Adventure World,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you'll have to get off once at Shirahama Station, but it shouldn't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll visit there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all your thoughtfulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came all the way here just to tell us about the market, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess she's just a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:30.69,Character Card,,0,0,0,,The next day\NRuins of Marine Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:39.03,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirarahama
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sandambeki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Adventure World
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tore Tore Market
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bus for Adventure World is the #3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next bus to Adventure World is at 10:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we've got 20 minutes left to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a stroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt like someone was watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want it so badly, why don't you buy it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look in the souvenir shop outside too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we've only got 7 or 8 minutes left, so we'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, would you mind if I stop over at the store of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time, you know. Hurry it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So you're going to buy it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone's watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up! The bus is gonna leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only one left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone other than Ran bought one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, that bus is headed for Sandambeki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Adventure World
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, wave, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's only a kid, and yet he's embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, it's you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'reâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji! Kota Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everyone else here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Three of them went out to sketch in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she was going to go for a drive until sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw her around 10:00 at Shirahama Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there! Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a laptop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you always carry it around with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Yura calls me a computer freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down and tell me again, Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this is Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is she and what happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the bushes at Sandambeki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a knife in her chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sandambeki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:55.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That suspicious person was on the bus to Sandambeki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all headed your way. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called the police already, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Yura and Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, I'll get in touch with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't we just pass the entrance to Sandambeki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is further inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Over there in the bushes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife stab through the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably died on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wallet is nowhere in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However you look at it, this seems to be a robbery-murder case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are no signs of a struggle nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a good chance the killer was an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I recall correctly, Maki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s keychain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...had the rental car key on it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:31.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does that mean the killer took it and fled in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this key chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:41.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Work gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does she have work gloves on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you time and time again not to mess around at crime scenes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's wait for the police to come before we investigate any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow! Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:01.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am O'ura from the Wakayama Prefectural Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ando, from the Shirahama East Police Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am honored to be able to work with you,\Nthe great detective Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:32.73,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective Ando (29)\NShirahama East\NPolice Station Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:32.73,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective O'ura (35)\NWakayama Prefectural\NPolice Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do give us precise advice if need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, cooperating with the police is the duty of any citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help in whatever way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let me introduce you to the friends of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kota Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who rushed over here with us from Adventure World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kanako Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who came over here from Engetsu Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Madoka Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who first found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is Tatsuhiko Yura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who came here from Shirarahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Madoka Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please tell us the circumstances under which you found Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard Beethoven playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beethoven?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sketching on the far end of Sandambeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I heard a cell phone ringtone playing from behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I went toward the bushes, where the sound was coming from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I called Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the place where Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was lying was fairly close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, you didn't notice that a crime was being committed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was facing the other way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the sound of the waves was rather loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you heard the cell phone's ringtone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Electronic sounds like those of cell phones are made to be audible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Ando, please give us a report on the autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is shock by a stab wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no sign of the corpse having been moved after death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the estimated time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in other words, the time the murder is thought to have been committed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,judging by the condition of the body, is between 9 and 11 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the time of the murder can be narrowed down a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at Shirahama Station at about ten minutes after 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was about 10:10?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After bowing to us, she left immediately in her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were going to get on the 10:15 bus headed for Adventure World,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm sure about the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to get from Shirahama Station to Sandambeki by car?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's tour season now, it should take less than 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's say it takes about 14 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she arrives at Sandambeki about 10:24.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she parks the car in the alley closest to the scene of the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would take her 2 minutes to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume she was killed immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the time the murder was committed would be around 10:26 at the earliest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can narrow it down to the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ca. 34 minutes between 10:26 and 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wallet seems to have disappeared from among her personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the car that the victim was thought to have been driving
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was found near Sansho Shrine, about 3 km away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An empty wallet was found inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Maki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we've already gotten to the bottom of this case. This case isâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the key of the car found?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the key was in the car's ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you only receive one key from the car rental shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think they usually give you two keys, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a robbery-murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After attacking Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the killer stole the car and fled in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then abandoned it near Sansho Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:21.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No. It's probably just made to look like a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's most likely that this murder was committed by an acquaintance of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the killer is among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so in order to contain the secret you decided to shut her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanki-Shirahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer must be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.17,0:24:31.22,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.22,0:24:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cosmetics
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.61,0:24:38.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, the solution! Figured out who did it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.82,0:24:40.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It has to be the person who bought Mr. Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.46,0:24:41.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That would be {\i1}you{\i0}!
